  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f28b81cd50761834ba1c489e4cae2022, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 15466676224
    m_Localized: Welcome! I will help you with your tasks. Begin by taking out the
      pan from the drawer in front of you and placing it on the stove.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 359189513945088
    m_Localized: 'Choose the language:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 454956702416896
    m_Localized: Do you need help?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 455177670934528
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1821029464981504
    m_Localized: Choose who will help you
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2917999210315776
    m_Localized: First of all, try to hang one of those hats on a hook.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2996685154467840
    m_Localized: Well done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2997274374488064
    m_Localized: Next exercise
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2998040191483904
    m_Localized: Quit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20653746548043776
    m_Localized: 'Take out the pan and place it on the stove

      Take out the
      carrot and place it on the cutting board

      Pick up the knife and slice
      the carrot into 15 pieces

      Place at least 10 carrot pieces inside the
      pan

      Turn on the stove

      Stir

      Turn off the stove'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 28029456270946304
    m_Localized: Congratulations, you did it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35281752365133824
    m_Localized: Language
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35283318497275904
    m_Localized: English
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35297609157898240
    m_Localized: 'Helper:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38116307870609408
    m_Localized: Now, take the carrot and place it on the cutting board.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38116575936966656
    m_Localized: Retrieve the knife from the drawer and slice the carrot into thin
      slices.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38116777192255488
    m_Localized: Now pick up the slices you just cut and put them inside the pan.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38117002959056896
    m_Localized: Turn on the stove by twisting the knob.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38117146123235328
    m_Localized: Now take the wooden spoon and stir the carrots so they don't burn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38117364529033216
    m_Localized: Lastly, turn the stove off.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38117493126393856
    m_Localized: Good job! You did it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39601379803066368
    m_Localized: Select a level
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39602542573187072
    m_Localized: Kitchen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39603541060808704
    m_Localized: Normal
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39603710896566272
    m_Localized: Hard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39604019874164736
    m_Localized: (With tips)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39604267912720384
    m_Localized: (Without tips)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39615849686298624
    m_Localized: Select the difficulty
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39845230123872256
    m_Localized: 'Choose your helper:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44343447024758784
    m_Localized: Do you want to start a new game?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44343866643902464
    m_Localized: New game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44344047175135232
    m_Localized: Saved game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 46515330184835072
    m_Localized: 'Name:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 46520638080741376
    m_Localized: 'Select your name:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 53626583944458240
    m_Localized: Do you want to go to the next exercise or would you rather stop
      for today?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55103769704591360
    m_Localized: Right
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55103913330143232
    m_Localized: Left
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55104083870543872
    m_Localized: 'Arm:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55543678508658688
    m_Localized: 'Environment:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55544335043063808
    m_Localized: Essential
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55544482552541184
    m_Localized: Detailed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55547917712683008
    m_Localized: None
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55550057118101504
    m_Localized: Back
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55811134359793664
    m_Localized: The arm you should use to complete the levels; you can also use
      your other arm (e.g., your left arm if you chose right and vice versa), but
      in that case you won't get any points.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55812115361361920
    m_Localized: You can choose between a simple environment, with less distractions
      to help you focus, or a more detailed environment, to increase realism and
      visual interest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55814168829685760
    m_Localized: You can choose a virtual helper to guide you through each level
      step by step. If you choose to have no helper you will get no hints to complete
      the level, so this option is recommended only if you have already mastered
      the levels, to add an extra challenge and get the expert trophies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63753283869011968
    m_Localized: 'Pull up the coffee machine''s lever

      Take a capsule from
      the container and put it in the machine

      Take a saucer from the cupboard
      and put it under the dispenser

      Take a cup from the cupboard and put
      it on the saucer

      Press the button to make coffee'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63880719684268032
    m_Localized: Coffee
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64839866022031360
    m_Localized: Hello! To make coffee, the first thing is to pull up the coffee
      machine's lever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64840159707197440
    m_Localized: Now, remove the lid from the jar and take a capsule.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64840314007252992
    m_Localized: Put the capsule in the machine, then pull the lever down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64840496107155456
    m_Localized: Open the cupboard's doors and take a saucer, then place it under
      the dispenser.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64840856930545664
    m_Localized: Take a cup and place it on the saucer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64840985775370240
    m_Localized: Lastly, press one of the buttons on the machine to dispense the
      coffee.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 72117449625366528
    m_Localized: What do you want to do?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 72121579135758336
    m_Localized: Back to the menu
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 77625558712119296
    m_Localized: Which level do you want to do?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 77625928762978304
    m_Localized: Living room
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 77310699189497856
    m_Localized: 'Spray the spots on the window

      (Sprayed spots: 0/10)

      Remove
      the spots with the sponge

      (Removed spots: 0/10)

      Remove the dust
      with the vacuum cleaner

      (Removed dust: 0/10)

      Throw the paper
      in the bin (Thrown paper: 0/10)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 78306396881743872
    m_Localized: Hello! The window is a bit dirty. To clean it, grab the spray bottle
      and spray all of the spots.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 78306842220359680
    m_Localized: Now, grab the sponge and wipe the window in order to eliminate the
      spots.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 78307112752967680
    m_Localized: Perfect! The floor needs some cleaning as well, so take the vacuum
      cleaner and push the button to turn it on.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 78307446606983168
    m_Localized: Vacuum the floor in order to remove all of the dust.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 78307779332730880
    m_Localized: 'Very good! Lastly, let''s tidy up the desk: grab all of the crumpled
      paper balls and throw them in the bin.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 81270040133300224
    m_Localized: 'Spray the spots on the window

      (Sprayed spots: 0/10)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 81270397378949120
    m_Localized: 'Remove the spots with the sponge

      (Removed spots: 0/10)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 81270608616681472
    m_Localized: 'Remove the dust with the vacuum cleaner

      (Removed dust: 0/10)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 81270747565584384
    m_Localized: 'Throw the paper in the bin (Thrown paper: 0/10)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
